title: Grateful Dead Live at Long Beach Arena on 1981-08-27
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC 24/96; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT; 24 bit to 16 bit with MusicConverter using sox-14-4-2
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Friend Of The Devil-> CC Rider, Peggy-O-> El Paso, Bird Song-> Passenger-> Cumberland Blues-> Looks Like Rain-> Might As Well

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Black Peter-> Good Lovin', E: Don't Ease Me In
